name: "Thanks Jelly" by Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
description: [Ballpoint pen on reclaimed cardboard with digital embellishments and color.] This piece was created as a "THANK YOU" to the individual (or robot or ghost or...) who's been buying a bunch of my weirdo art! It's a 1 of 1! Do with it as you will!!! ---Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
